_sText:
A new skill surfmap by Rapsodia, HellRaisedSurfer & me. 
Thanks to all betatesters and Surf-Velocity for hosting the beta-test.

Included are:
-6 "normal" stages
-1 Bonus
-jail+spawn
-timersystem
  --you got 90s for each level, if you beat one, you get another 90sec for the level after. once the 90s ran out, all will get teleported to jail.

The map has been made for tick 66 and sv_airaccelerate 150. 
Included weapons are knives, usp, deagle, TMP and ak47. How you get each? find out.

Furthermore, thanks to Sangre for all the tips he gave me. And thanks to copy-mark for making this awesome vid:
